					<a href="http://en.gravatar.com/site/signup" class="gravatar"><img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar.php?gravatar_id=53d91af100208c5c7a1ec8b31c46bc14&size=31&rating=R&d=identicon" alt="" /></a>					<div>
